race.description: Trackside Pet Meats Pick 6 (N/P) Stake Pr2 Divisio
race.comment: BLUE KHAKI (8) has found the frame here at the last couple of runs when prominent throughout, most recently when second beaten half a length (23.32). Goes well this circuit with four wins and two minors. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Leading chance again. MANNER OF STRIFE (1) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 6 lengths at Angle Park in a handy 19.69 beating Spear Ruler. Likely to be in the finish. BLUE TO BURN (5) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing sixth (24.16) in a Other at this track. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Must be included in calculations. KIWI TO BURN (2) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.
